title: Just a spirits store for longer than wine, wine stores for longer than beer.  Also, if I'm remembering it correctly and should believe chat gpt, wine was used to sterilize wounds, but beer wasn't. Indeed beer can't, although it would be safer to wash a wound with beer than to wash it with crap ancient water.
